ork_count`) + compute demotion + validator override-gate + scorecard partial path change + `migrate-v1.1-to-v1.2.py`. Under-a-week deliverable. Post-V1.2 watchpoints (V1.3 and V1.2.x) logged in CONSOLIDATION §8 (override-pattern telemetry trigger: 3 V1.2 scans shipped; 11-scan comparator analysis trigger: V1.2 frozen + telemetry + ≥11 V1.2 scans; community-norms enum expansion trigger: ≥3 missing-qualitative-context overrides citing community norms).
